Session Has been cancelledBill NonPrivilegedpst Bill Dispatcher Training Session scheduled for July in Salt Lake City Utah has been cancelled with only people signed up and only three people with hotel reservations IF YOU HAVE MADE RESERVATIONS BE SURE TO CANCEL THEM ASAP Bert Meyers and Mark Guzman were registered for this class There are currently six spaces available in the Session scheduled for July in Folsom CA Please contact Danielle at or if you would like to attend this class Preference will be given to those who were enrolled in the July class for the remaining spaces Danielle Gardner PH Fax EM
